# Laravel Social Media App

A simple social media-like web application built using **Laravel**, where users can:

- Create accounts and log in/out
- Follow/unfollow other users
- Create and manage posts
- Comment on posts
- Admin can control users and content from a dedicated panel

## Features

- User Registration and Login (Authentication)
- Profile creation and editing
- Follow / Unfollow system
- Post creation, editing, deletion
- Commenting on posts
- Admin panel for user/content management
- Responsive UI using Bootstrap (or any frontend framework used)

