## Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/laravel-social-app.git
cd laravel-social-

### install dependencies
composer install
npm install && npm run dev   # Only if you're using frontend tools

##setup environment  
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
## run migratoin and seed 
php artisan migrate
php artisan db:seed
## start server 
php artisan serve
